---
import ContactForm from './ContactForm.astro';
---

<section class="hero">
    <div class="container hero-content">
      
      <!-- 1. The Context (Small, top) -->
      <div class="hero-header fade-in text-center mb-6">
        <p class="tagline-context tagline-subtle">Automatización con IA para empresas que no quieren seguir en modo “supervivencia”.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 2. The Core Problem (H1) -->
      <div class="hero-title-block mb-16 px-4 text-center">
        <h1 class="main-jail-title">
            Tu empresa, <span class="jail-gradient">¿cárcel de tareas...</span> <br class="hidden md:block">
            <span class="secondary-title text-center">o el activo que debería ser?</span>
        </h1>
      </div>

      <!-- 3. The Narrative (Tension) -->
      <div class="narrative-container mb-20 px-4">
        <div class="narrative-consolidated fade-in delay-1 text-center">
            <div class="narrative-segment mb-4">
                <p>Cierras el portátil. La oficina casi vacía. Sales tarde, otra vez.</p>
                <p>¡aaaah!, ¿de verdad ahora? Te acuerdas de esa tarea pendiente. La que sabes hacer con los ojos cerrados, pero te va a robar un par de horas.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="narrative-segment mb-4">
                <p>De repente, el cuerpo se llena de una sensación incómoda. La tarea ya es lo de menos. El texto está escrito: <span class="text-emphasis">“No llego a la cena.”</span> Pero tu dedo no se mueve y no es por el cansancio. Es lo que te espera al llegar a casa: ese silencio, esa nada.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="narrative-impact mb-6">
                <p class="emotional-danger">Joder… el daño que hace: <br> <span class="indifference-text">esa indiferencia debería considerarse arma blanca</span></p>
            </div>

            <div class="narrative-transition">
                <p class="transition-text">Si has llegado hasta aquí y esto te suena, lo que viene ahora te interesa. Es algo más que motivación barata.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 4. The Promise (High Contrast Peak) -->
      <div class="solution-peak text-center mb-20 fade-in delay-11">
        <h2 class="hero-promise-title">
            <span class="mega-gradient">Es una salida: 4 datos. Una demo. Sin humo.</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <!-- 5. Branding & Context -->
      <div class="hero-footer-branding mb-20 fade-in delay-11 text-center">
         <div class="branding-footer">
            <h2 class="company-title-large gradient-text-silver text-center">El club de la mente fría</h2>
            <p class="slogan-footer gradient-text-silver text-center">Automatizamos procesos con IA para que tu empresa funcione sin que tengas que estar encima de todo.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- 6. Form -->
      <div class="hero-form-wrapper">
        <ContactForm 
            title="Muéstrame cómo funcionaría en mi empresa" 
            subtitle='Rellena el formulario y vemos tu negocio a lo "mente-fría".' 
            cta="Quítame tareas de encima"
            id="hero"
        />
      </div>

    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .hero {
        padding-top: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
        padding-bottom: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem); /* Reduced padding to connect with Vision */
    }
    .tagline-context { 
        font-size: 1.1rem; 
        color: var(--brand-pink); 
        font-weight: 600; 
        letter-spacing: 0.02em; 
        white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .tagline-subtle {
        font-weight: 300;
        color: var(--text);
        opacity: 0.4;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }
    @media (max-width: 960px) {
        .tagline-context { white-space: normal; }
    }

    /* Titles */
    .main-jail-title { 
        font-family: var(--ff-display); font-weight: 700; 
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem); line-height: 1.05; margin: 0; 
        letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }
    .jail-gradient {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-purple) 20%, #ba49ce 50%, var(--brand-pink) 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        background-clip: text;
        color: transparent;
        display: inline-block;
    }
    .secondary-title {
        font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight: 700; display: block; margin-top: 0.5rem;
        font-family: var(--ff-display);
        opacity: 0.9;
    }

    /* Narrative Consolidada */
    .narrative-container { max-width: 850px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
    .narrative-consolidated p { 
        font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 1.8vw, 1.35rem); 
        color: var(--muted); 
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        line-height: 1.1;
        font-weight: 500;
        letter-spacing: -0.01em;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .text-emphasis { color: var(--text); font-weight: 700; font-style: italic; }
    
    .narrative-segment { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .narrative-impact { margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
    
    .emotional-danger { 
        font-size: 1.25rem !important; 
        color: var(--text) !important;
        line-height: 1.2 !important;
    }
    .indifference-text {
        font-style: italic;
        opacity: 0.9;
        font-size: 1.1em;
    }

    .transition-text {
        color: var(--text) !important;
        font-size: 1.25rem !important;
        line-height: 1.4 !important;
    }

    /* Promise Peak */

    .hero-promise-title {
        font-family: var(--ff-display);
        font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 8vw, 6.5rem);
        line-height: 0.9;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -0.06em;
        margin-top: 1rem;
    }
    .mega-gradient {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 20%, var(--brand-purple) 60%, #ba49ce 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        background-clip: text;
        color: transparent;
        display: inline-block;
        filter: drop-shadow(0 0 30px rgba(186, 73, 206, 0.4));
    }
    :global(.theme-light) .mega-gradient {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000 20%, var(--brand-purple) 70%, #ba49ce 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        background-clip: text;
    }

    /* Branding Footer */
    .branding-footer {
        opacity: 0.9;
    }
    .company-title-large { 
        font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 7vw, 5.6rem); /* Increased size (+40% approx from 4rem base) */
        font-family: var(--ff-display); 
        font-weight: 800; 
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
        margin-top: -0.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .slogan-footer {
        font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); /* Reduced size (-30% approx from 4rem base) */
        font-family: var(--ff-display);
        font-weight: 600;
        line-height: 1.2;
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .gradient-text-silver {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--text) 0%, color-mix(in oklab, var(--text) 30%, transparent) 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        background-clip: text;
        color: transparent;
    }

    /* Form Card Refined */
    .form-card {
        width: 100%; max-width: 650px;
        background: color-mix(in oklab, var(--surface) 80%, transparent);
        backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        padding: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
        box-shadow: 0 40px 80px -20px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
        border-radius: 32px;
    }
    :global(.theme-light) .form-card {
        border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
        background: #ffffff;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 40px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    .form-title { margin: 0; font-size: 2.2rem; color: var(--text); font-family: var(--ff-display); font-weight: 700; }
    .form-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .form-header p { margin: 0.5rem 0 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 1.1rem; }
    .form-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.25rem; }
    .span-full { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
    .label-text { display: block; font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; }
    .privacy-wrapper .label-text { display: inline; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle; cursor: pointer;}
    
    input[type="text"], input[type="email"] { 
        width: 100%; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); 
        border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1rem 1.2rem; 
        font-family: var(--ff-body); font-size: 1.1rem; transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    input:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--brand-purple); box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px color-mix(in oklab, var(--brand-purple) 20%, transparent); }
    
    /* Circular Checkbox Styles */
    .checkbox-container {
        display: block;
        position: relative;
        padding-left: 35px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        cursor: pointer;
        user-select: none;
    }
    .checkbox-container input {
        position: absolute;
        opacity: 0;
        cursor: pointer;
        height: 0;
        width: 0;
    }
    .checkmark {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        height: 24px;
        width: 24px;
        background-color: var(--bg);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 50%;
        transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .checkbox-container:hover input ~ .checkmark {
        border-color: var(--brand-purple);
    }
    .checkbox-container input:checked ~ .checkmark {
        background-color: var(--brand-purple);
        border-color: var(--brand-purple);
    }
    .checkmark:after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        display: none;
    }
    .checkbox-container input:checked ~ .checkmark:after {
        display: block;
    }
    .checkbox-container .checkmark:after {
        left: 8px;
        top: 4px;
        width: 5px;
        height: 10px;
        border: solid white;
        border-width: 0 2px 2px 0;
        transform: rotate(45deg);
    }
    .full-width { width: 100%; justify-content: center; padding: 1.2rem; font-size: 1.2rem; margin-top: 1rem; color: white !important; }
    .form-footer { font-size: 1rem !important; }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .form-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .main-jail-title { font-size: 2.1rem; line-height: 1.1; }
        .secondary-title { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
        .hero-promise-title { font-size: 2.8rem; }
        .form-title { font-size: 1.8rem; }
        .hero { padding: var(--s-6) 0; }
        .form-card { padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 24px; }
        .narrative-container { padding: 0 1rem; }
        .narrative-block p { font-size: 1.15rem; }
    }
    
    .fade-in { opacity: 0; animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out forwards; transform: translateY(10px); }
    @keyframes fadeIn { to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
    .delay-1 { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
    .delay-2 { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
    .delay-3 { animation-delay: 0.8s; }
    .delay-4 { animation-delay: 1.2s; }
    .delay-5 { animation-delay: 1.4s; }
    .delay-6 { animation-delay: 1.8s; }
    .delay-7 { animation-delay: 2.2s; }
    .delay-8 { animation-delay: 2.5s; }
    .delay-9 { animation-delay: 3.0s; }
    .delay-10 { animation-delay: 3.3s; }
    .delay-11 { animation-delay: 3.8s; }
    .delay-12 { animation-delay: 4.2s; }
    .delay-13 { animation-delay: 4.8s; }
    .delay-14 { animation-delay: 5.2s; }
    .delay-15 { animation-delay: 6.0s; }
</style>
